{"type":"message","id":"34746c3f","parentId":"b905c5c4","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:50:53.671Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've completed the self-learning task. The learning notes have been saved to the memory file.","thinkingSignature":"0e3e09a47b5a81016ce691034ed697b5f460a8be185778934f46fbe7fb7d1e43"},{"type":"text","text":"自主学习已完成，整理了3个维度的行业关键信息并保存至 `memory/学习笔记.md`：\n\n1. **企业数字化转型**：数据要素价值释放、新质生产力成为焦点，混合云+边缘计算成主流架构，广东/北京等地设定明确转型目标\n2. **智能安防**：AIoT深度融合+主动预判成核心竞争力，数字孪生普及率超60%，工程交付向运维服务转型\n3. **IT运维与网络集成**：2026年政企市场突破2800亿元，AIOps规模化应用，一站式运维平台成区域政企主流选择"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4842,"output":148,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48971,"cost":{"input":0.0014525999999999999,"output":0.00017759999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00294963}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775105448423}}
